{"tid":1604623,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"81年首次！AC米蘭前6輪輸4場","createTime":"2019-09-30T04:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T17:57:23.000Z","uid":173952,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"5b68681b98b7ada7f58d03567e18f63cf6361de9","tid":1604623,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:31:31.000Z","msg":"又輸了<br />\n<br />\n  意甲第6輪，AC米蘭主場戰費倫天拿。上半場賓拿沙（Ismael Bennacer）送點，普爾加罰中。下半場穆沙基奧（M.Musacchio）染紅，卡斯度彭利拿維利擴大優勢，賓拿沙再送點小基艾沙（Federico Chiesa）射失，列貝利（Franck Ribery）梅開二度，特奧（Theo Hernandez）一條龍扳回一球！最終，AC米蘭1-3費倫天拿慘遭3連敗。今場戰罷，AC米蘭6分第16，僅高出降班區1分。<br />\n<br />\n  意甲聯賽，AC米蘭主場1-3不敵費倫天拿，紅黑軍團前6輪輸了4場，近81年來首次。<br />\n<br />\n  AC米蘭主場1-3不敵費倫天拿，遭遇聯賽3連敗，前6輪意甲過後，米蘭積分僅為6分。降至積分榜第16位，僅比降班區第18名的熱那亞高1分。<br />\n<br />\n  意甲第6輪，米蘭主場1比3不敵費倫天拿，前6輪比賽輸掉4場。據全市場透露，米蘭球會考慮解僱詹保羅（Marco Giampaolo），並已經聯繫了烏克蘭教練舒夫真高（Andriy Shevchenko），詢問他是否有意接手米蘭。<br />\n<br />\n  米蘭對陣費倫天拿，第77分鐘，小基艾沙送出助攻，列貝利帶球後展現出色個人能力，禁區內靈巧一扣晃開米蘭後防，射門得手幫助球隊繼續擴大比數。"},{"pid":"19b1b8e0ceaad590599af1285a64b8f31b73b145","tid":1604623,"uid":52571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"撚蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe6596842b81d3b0b5ec9fd9b9673164d8eb7cf","tid":1604623,"uid":99861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19b1b8e0ceaad590599af1285a64b8f31b73b145","tid":1604623,"uid":52571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"撚蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe06f2d3eab2cbea0973a6b2d369f356f9b4ea5","tid":1604623,"uid":67225,"like":0,